<p style="margin: 0 0 16px;">Dear <%= @resource.name.presence || "fountain pen enthusiast" %>!</p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 16px;">
  Either you or someone else has requested to change the password for your account
  on Fountain Pen Companion. If it was you, please use the button below to set a new password:
</p>

<%= render "layouts/mailer_button", url: edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token), text: "Change my password" %>

<p style="margin: 0 0 16px; color: #666666; font-size: 14px;">If you didn't request a change to your password, please ignore this email.</p>

<p style="margin: 0;">Thanks,<br />The Fountain Pen Capybara</p>
